title: Logos Round 3! [Deadline: Feb 16]
author: ebullient
content: We're on to round 3! If you go back and look, we did end up clustering (first two rows) and clumping (a few variants of B). [Round 3 various sizes and context](https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/12WH8bufO0gx5_B9Lz5Hg-b0BJSWysbw1s8Xt--kWOg8/edit?usp=sharing), [large image 1](https://design.jboss.org/commonhaus/images/commonhaus_r3v1_large.png), [large image 2](https://design.jboss.org/commonhaus/images/commonhaus_r3v2_large.png), [large image 3](https://design.jboss.org/commonhaus/images/commonhaus_r3v3_large.png) Remember: We still thinking about concepts here.
